description: Capacity Development for SCTM II phase

subproject.description:
Output 1) SCTM is modern association of local governments, capable to deliver high level services to member municipalities (based on in-depth evaluations from the beginning and the end of the SCTM II) 

Output 2) Benchamark system and training programme that has been developed and implemented in selected municipalities in Serbia and Montenegro improved delivery of services for at least 15 % (municipal capacity index-type tool tailored for municipalities in Serbia)
subproject.title: Capacity Development for SCTM
